<h1>Clean stream it!</h1>
<br/>Offering edited google play/amazon prime etc. (ask for netflix/hulu)<
<br/>
See <a href=https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/clean-editing-movie-player>our google group</a> to discuss it.
